reviewText: He was a great entertainer. I enjoyed watching it.
Sinatra is, was and always will DEFINITELY be the GREATEST entertainer of all time and who's ever lived and will live. There's no performer on Earth like Frank Sinatra. :D

MY WHOLE FAMILY REALLY ENJOYED THIS FILM. I GREW UP WITH MY FATHER PLAYING FRANK SINATRA MUSIC AND I STILL LOVE HIM TO THIS DAY. THIS FILM REALLY SHOWS WHAT FRANK WAS LIKE AS HE GREW MORE FAMOUS AND HAS GREAT FOOTAGE OF HIS PERSONAL AND PUBLIC LIFE. VERY WELL DONE.
